**Differentiate between `next()` and `nextLine()` methods of the `Scanner` class.**

**Model Answer (3 marks):**

| Aspect | `next()` | `nextLine()` |
|--------|----------|--------------|
| Reads | A single **token** (word) | An entire **line** of text |
| Stops at | Whitespace (space, tab, newline) | Newline character (`\n`) |
| Return type | `String` | `String` |
| Use-case | Single-word inputs (e.g., username) | Multi-word inputs (e.g., full name) |
| Example input | `"Rahul Kumar"` → reads only `"Rahul"` | `"Rahul Kumar"` → reads `"Rahul Kumar"` |

