> **Legend (UML standard, used in KTU answers):**
> - `-` (minus) → **`private`** member
> - `#` (hash) → **`protected`** member
> - `+` (plus) → **`public`** member

## 4.2 Access Decision Flowchart

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Access Request to Member M] --> B{Is requester in SameClass?}
    B -- Yes --> Z1[GRANTED]
    B -- No --> C{Is requester a declared Friend?}
    C -- Yes --> Z1
    C -- No --> D{Is M declared public?}
    D -- Yes --> Z1
    D -- No --> E{Is M declared protected AND requester in DerivedClass?}
    E -- Yes --> Z1
    E -- No --> F[DENIED - Compile Error]

    Z1 --> X[Access Permitted]
    F --> Y[Compiler Error: 'M is private/protected within this context']
```

