## 3.4 Analytical Matrix — Common Errors and Fixes

| Error Message | Root Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `ClassNotFoundException: com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver` | MySQL Connector/J JAR not in classpath. | Add the JAR via IDE or `javac -cp .:mysql-connector.jar`. |
| `SQLException: Communications link failure` | DB server not running or wrong port. | Start MySQL server; verify port `3306`. |
| `SQLException: Access denied for user` | Wrong username/password. | Re-check credentials. |
| `SQLSyntaxErrorException` | SQL has a typo (missing comma, wrong keyword). | Test the SQL directly in a DB client. |
| `SQLException: No suitable driver found` | URL format doesn't match any loaded driver. | Use correct URL pattern (e.g., `jdbc:mysql://...`). |
| `NumberFormatException` in roll-no field | User typed non-numeric data. | Wrap `parseInt` in try-catch. |
